<h1 class="heading-36">Can you get Carer's Allowance?</h1>

<p>You must meet these requirements before you can get Carer's Allowance:<p>


<ol class="steps">
  <li><p>You are aged 16 or over</p></li>

  <li><p>You live in England, Scotland, Wales or <span id="these-countries" class="js-toggle link-style" data-hide="#these-countries" data-show=".country-toggle">these countries</span><span class="js-hidden country-toggle">these countries:</span>

      <ul class="country-toggle js-hidden list-bullet" style="margin-top: 10px">
        <li>if you live in Northern Ireland go to <a href="#">NI Carers Allowance</a></li>
        <li>families of HM Forces can apply from any country</li>
        <li>if you live in the European Economic Area (EEA) or Switzerland you may still qualify</li>
      </ul>

      </p>
  </li>
<!--
  <li><p>You live in England, Scotland, Wales or if:</span>

      <ul class="list-bullet" style="margin-top: 10px">
        <li>you live in Northern Ireland - go to <a href="#">NI Carers Allowance</a></li>
        <li>you're family of HM Forces you can apply from any country</li>
        <li>you live in the European Economic Area (EEA) or Switzerland you may still qualify</li>
      </ul>

      </p>
  </li>
